snippet.title: The Expanse: A Telltale Series - Episode 3: First Ones Trailer
snippet.description:
The trail that started with the U.N.N. Urshinabi wreckage leads the crew of The Artemis to a mysterious, abandoned station. No records, save for a mysterious message and what’s left behind await Drummer in the depths of the station. Is there something they could still salvage inside? Maybe the facility’s MK Core holds some answers. 

Episode 3 of The Expanse: A Telltale Series is OUT NOW!
